                            <div data-answer="F"><p>2. The market is doing badly because of the conflict in Gaza.</p><label><input type="radio" name="p2q2" value="T">T</label><label><input type="radio" name="p2q2" value="F">F</label><div class="feedback"></div></div>
                            <div data-answer="T"><p>3. The Israeli stock market is up 80% since October 2023.</p><label><input type="radio" name="p2q3" value="T">T</label><label><input type="radio" name="p2q3" value="F">F</label><div class="feedback"></div></div>
                            <div data-answer="F"><p>4. Investors from other countries are not buying in the Israeli market.</p><label><input type="radio" name="p2q4" value="T">T</label><label><input type="radio" name="p2q4" value="F">F</label><div class="feedback"></div></div>
                            <div data-answer="T"><p>5. If the AI boom ends, the market could have a problem.</p><label><input type="radio" name="p2q5" value="T">T</label><label><input type="radio" name="p2q5" value="F">F</label><div class="feedback"></div></div>
                        </div>
